      Tropical treats with tastes that tease, the Mango Swirl makes a perfect match with the persimmon fruit non-dairy ice cream base. <br><br>
Rounded and full, but pleasantly refreshing – if your guests are extra spoilt, you may even leave them some!!
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm">
     Passionfruit lovers just won’t be able to get enough of this, with is creamy like, smooth persimmon fruit base, where the Passionfruit Swirl dances the distance. It’s nothing less than moreish and nothing short of a pure delight. Recommendation – use a small spoon or it will go too quickly!!!
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm">
      Deliciously creamy and refreshingly smooth, Summer Berry Swirl teases your taste buds all the way to the bottom of the tub. The burst of strawberry, blueberry and raspberry, make this persimmon fruit based non-dairy ice cream, something else, and leaves you wanting more!
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm">
       This persimmon based non-dairy ice cream is the quintessential kiwianna ‘ice creamy’ with its Kiwifruit Swirl partying with your palette (without the fatty after taste of dairy). Kiwifruit Swirl runs the perfect play with the persimmon – it’s just healthy indulgency!
